{"tid":2434444,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"其實剝智慧齒唔係咁可怕","createTime":"2021-03-05T14:01:50.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-09T06:47:58.000Z","uid":378158,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a16d11af9e61f504d44addbc4a0db137a81c231b","tid":2434444,"uid":378158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T14:01:50.000Z","msg":"牙痛慘過大病，今日最終鼓起勇氣去左剝智慧齒，小弟生平最怕睇牙醫，早晚刷牙仲會用牙線 <br />\n但不幸出智慧齒痛，原本以為剝智慧齒好閒事，所以求其Google 搵左間屋企附近嘅牙醫去睇睇，話我智慧齒係橫生仲要好近神經線，係佢到剝吾到要轉介，痛咗幾日真係頂唔順約左連登牙醫鄧幹耀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好好彩咁啱有位睇到急症<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n聽人講剝智慧齒個下好撚痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tmHxBEA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtmHxBEA.jpg&h=765113b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n 登記完問咗身體情況簽左份術前同意書，由於我之前個牙醫冇俾番X Ray我，我就去左鄧醫生度照，照完X Ray後，姑娘就叫我坐低等叫名，個刻真係好撚煎熬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n around等一個鐘左右。叫名入房見醫生，訓係手術床度，比醫生照完，話我左面下顎隻智慧齒同神經線好近，手術會幾辛苦同埋好腫<br />\n<br />\n醫生幫我Check完後隨即打麻醉藥再開刀剝牙，因為打左麻醉，無乜痛感，係痺痺地，Feel到隻牙好實好難拎出黎，最後隻牙整碎曬，拎左出來。睇番手錶做左大約6分鐘，無諗過快成咁。<br />\n<br />\n埋單Total：$4600<br />\n$3800手術費<br />\n$500 X Ray<br />\n$300醫生檢查 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WELfzsO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWELfzsO.jpg&h=e22a6b37&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n番到屋企麻醉開始過，有少少痛，可接受。食左雪糕，又食左通粉。總結：剝智慧齒其實都唔係咁驚，同埋鄧醫生真係好熟手。"},{"pid":"888b957604bb16e6e736056eb9ef837c0dc157df","tid":2434444,"uid":22692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T14:04:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ce519ecffb4b66259ad44e50a05e08f2ba313ea","tid":2434444,"uid":71237,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T14:05:14.000Z","msg":"剝牙問題一律建議鄧幹耀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"133da89151cf984513dc085a2ac01f3af922047e","tid":2434444,"uid":378158,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8ce519ecffb4b66259ad44e50a05e08f2ba313ea","tid":2434444,"uid":71237,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T14:05:14.000Z","msg":"剝牙問題一律建議鄧幹耀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T15:35:16.000Z","msg":"係，手勢好好，幾分鐘既事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8e14641a025a510dacce534f2ba4c9ee62c9507","tid":2434444,"uid":226768,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T08:51:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3221baa9d0bf74271621b5802a4ff1a121f50445","tid":2434444,"uid":52423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T08:53:50.000Z","msg":"打麻醉針嗰下最痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98a7f54bafa7f3ab8fe5b45ba137cb59e1c19865","tid":2434444,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T09:18:55.000Z","msg":"操返越玩越輕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33b19896d1a8be80f85a151b5543d3de0d4161e7","tid":2434444,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"98a7f54bafa7f3ab8fe5b45ba137cb59e1c19865","tid":2434444,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T09:18:55.000Z","msg":"操返越玩越輕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T09:19:57.000Z","msg":"錯post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src